title: Korean Drama - My Girl [Korean with English Subs][Full Episodes]
description:
Synopsis

When Seol Gong Chan Lee Dong Wook meets the lively and beautiful Yu Rin Lee Da Hae, he finds out that she has connections to his missing cousin, who his grandfather has been searching for a long time. He asks Yu Rin to lie about being his long missing cousin until he can find his real cousin. She says yes, but soon their feelings for each other get in the way of their plans. Gong Chan&#039;s friend Jung Woo Lee Joon Ki falls for Yu Rin while Gong Chan&#039;s ex girlfriend, Seo Hyun Park Si Yeon, a pro tennis player, tries to win him back. Will the two ever tell each other how they feel? Will Gong Chan ever find his real cousin? My Girl was a Top Ten hit in Korea in 2006, aided by the appearance of hot new actor, Lee Joon Ki.
